paragraph.value: report brief results on SQuAD (Table 3),  We also evaluate the SynNet on the NewsQAto-SQuAD direction. We directly apply the best setting from the other direction and report the result in Table 3.  The SynNet improves over the baseline by 1.6% in EM and 0.7% in F1. Limited by space, we leave out ablation studies in this direction.
